{"tid":2200631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"牛津大學研究顯示，臺灣在武肺期間的表現，反駁了政府要保公共健康，還是要保經濟的偽命題","createTime":"2020-09-13T06:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T08:15:37.000Z","uid":294518,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9bf3926f166d690bc90496784405a4b0d6d504a0","tid":2200631,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:12:39.000Z","msg":"CORONAVIRUS/Taiwan disproves 'health or economy' COVID-19 argument: study<br />\n<a href=\"https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202009120002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffocustaiwan.tw%2Fsociety%2F202009120002&d=O8bnHDCsQiwN1SoPxP513eIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=e379d83a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://focustaiwan.tw/society/202009120002</a><br />\n<br />\nTaipei, Sept. 12 (CNA) Taiwan is one of several countries that clearly disproves the argument that governments must choose between protecting people's health and protecting the economy in their responses to the COVID-19 pandemic, according to research from Oxford University.<br />\n9月12日，台灣台北（CNA），根據牛津大學的研究，應對COVID-19大流行，台灣採取的措施明確反駁：政府必須在保護人民健康或保護經濟之間做出取舍這一偽命題。"},{"pid":"d2f0ac7593135c0417e8316295f0267d5133118b","tid":2200631,"uid":231583,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:13:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c27dd59c5dd8e6839ef2fa677f16e8bcf1c58d85","tid":2200631,"uid":198258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:15:05.000Z","msg":"Taiwan No.1"},{"pid":"55e2dd6965483d119c781ccad16a3fa0586cc573","tid":2200631,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:17:00.000Z","msg":"係一個有民主制度嘅國家，當政者既政策一定有好有壞<br />\n<br />\n明知道有武廢，人民應該都要自己做好保護配合"},{"pid":"7998e3e59bcbfe824b8b38a025add46e4e1e351b","tid":2200631,"uid":342398,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T06:21:57.000Z","msg":"台灣今次簡直係role model"},{"pid":"acda377c8ebaa0c825fa66226088217bd5152bf5","tid":2200631,"uid":2